                {
                    "id": 4509365,
                    "topic_id": "CP_50515376",
                    "parent_id": 4509336,
                    "target_id": 4509336,
                    "user_id": "29968040",
                    "reply_user_id": "17025146",
                    "content": "那看来你和我想的一样，只是我目前在一个关键部位卡住了\n在html渲染文字时，会把一大段文字分割成一个个词来渲染（大概上以空格分词\n这样，当某个文本长度超过渲染区域长度，会直接把一整个词挪到下一行\n但是，这个“分词系统”的具体工作原理是什么呢\n网上的说法：每个全角字符单独成词\n英文以“-”和空格分隔\n例如：&apos;abc def-ghi&apos;会分成&apos;abc &apos;,&apos;def-&apos;,&apos;ghi&apos;\n",
                    "likes": 0,
                    "unlikes": 0,
                    "replies": 0,
                    "top": 0,
                    "removed": 0,
                    "links": null,
                    "created_at": "2024-01-24 22:29:13",
                    "comment_from": "message",
                    "username": "黄羿杰",
                    "user_avatar_path": "https://static0.xesimg.com/udc-o-user-avatar/20210410/TalzTGb2L3-6e1wkJImvuYvwEQ1154.jpg",
                    "reply_username": "吴宇航",
                    "emojis": [],
                    "is_like": false,
                    "is_unlike": false,
                    "is_topic_author_like": false,
                    "is_topic_author_reply": true,
                    "can_delete": true,
                    "can_top": false,
                    "user_profile": null
                },
                {
                    "id": 4509366,
                    "topic_id": "CP_50515376",
                    "parent_id": 4509336,
                    "target_id": 4509336,
                    "user_id": "29968040",
                    "reply_user_id": "17025146",
                    "content": "然而，当文本复杂时，这个说法就不对了\n比如&apos;哈哈哈-111aaa&apos;会分成&apos;哈&apos;,&apos;哈&apos;,&apos;哈-111aaa&apos;\n所以我需要更详细的分词逻辑",
                    "likes": 0,
                    "unlikes": 0,
                    "replies": 0,
                    "top": 0,
                    "removed": 0,
                    "links": null,
                    "created_at": "2024-01-24 22:29:45",
                    "comment_from": "topic",
                    "username": "黄羿杰",
                    "user_avatar_path": "https://static0.xesimg.com/udc-o-user-avatar/20210410/TalzTGb2L3-6e1wkJImvuYvwEQ1154.jpg",
